Exile's Path
	TYPE:General
	PRERACE:1,Half-elf
	DESC:A lifetime spent shunned by others and eschewing your heritage makes you resistant to efforts to pry inside of your mind.
	SOURCEPAGE:p.47
	BENEFIT:Once per day, when you fail a Will save against an enchantment spell or effect, you may reroll that saving throw, but must take the reroll result even if it's worse.

Half-Drow Paragon
	TYPE:General
